razor eaters is a 2003 australian crime thriller film written and directed by shannon young . the film had its world premiere on 13 july 2003 at the melbourne underground film festival , and later had a dvd release in july 2006 . it follows an anarchist street gang ( based on the real-life &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) who terrorize those whom they believe deserve punishment . razor eaters was met with some controversy , as the melbourne police department labeled it as " extremely violent " and " obscene " when it was first released in 2003 .